metadata.name: IN CHOCO MOON (WHEN THE DOG SAW YOU)
metadata.description:
In the planet  “Choco moon”, once in a while, dogs can meet owners. This artwork represents the feeling that they met. It’s the moment of happiness. Do you know? How are dog’s acting when they see you! 🐶🌕💖

2000 x 2500 PX
Animation 12 sec | 300 dpi
